---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "About Us | Chicago Executive Car Service";
const description = "Learn about Chicago's premier executive car service. Over 15 years of experience providing luxury corporate transportation to Fortune 500 companies and executives.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          About Chicago Executive Car Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300">
          Chicago's premier choice for executive transportation since 2009
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Founded in 2009, Chicago Executive Car Service was built on a simple premise: corporate executives and business professionals deserve transportation that matches their standards for excellence, reliability, and professionalism.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          What started as a small operation with three vehicles and a commitment to exceptional service has grown into Chicago's most trusted executive car service, serving over 500 corporate accounts and completing more than 50,000 successful trips. Our growth is a testament to our unwavering focus on reliability, professionalism, and client satisfaction.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Today, we maintain a diverse fleet of luxury vehicles and employ a team of professional chauffeurs who understand that every trip is an opportunity to exceed expectations. We serve Fortune 500 companies, leading law firms, financial institutions, and thousands of individual executives who demand the best.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-amber-500 mb-2">15+</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Years in Business</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Serving Chicago since 2009</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-amber-500 mb-2">500+</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Corporate Clients</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Including Fortune 500 companies</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-amber-500 mb-2">50K+</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Trips Completed</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Maintaining 98% on-time rate</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Our Values</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Reliability Above All</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We understand that missed flights, late arrivals to meetings, and transportation uncertainties are unacceptable in business. Our 98% on-time rate reflects our commitment to reliability. We use advanced flight tracking, real-time traffic monitoring, and maintain backup vehicles to ensure you arrive on time, every time.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Professional Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Every chauffeur undergoes comprehensive training, background checks, and continuous evaluation. They understand that they represent not just our company, but yours as well. Professional attire, courteous service, and discretion are non-negotiable standards for our team.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Client-First Service</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We succeed when you succeed. This philosophy drives every decision we make, from vehicle selection to route planning to customer support. Your dedicated account manager is empowered to solve problems and exceed expectations, not just meet minimum standards.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Transparency & Integrity</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              No hidden fees, no surprises, no excuses. We provide transparent pricing, detailed invoicing, and honest communication. If we make a mistake, we own it and make it right immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Continuous Improvement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              The transportation industry evolves, and so do we. We invest in the latest technology, maintain our vehicles to the highest standards, and continuously train our team. Client feedback drives our improvement efforts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Why Clients Choose Us</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">✓ Proven Track Record</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Over 15 years serving Chicago's business community with consistent 5-star service and a 98% on-time rate.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">✓ Professional Chauffeurs</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Extensively trained, background-checked professionals who understand corporate transportation needs.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">✓ Premium Fleet</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Late-model luxury vehicles maintained to the highest standards and cleaned after every trip.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">✓ 24/7 Availability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Round-the-clock service, 365 days a year, because business doesn't operate on a 9-to-5 schedule.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">✓ Technology-Enabled</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Flight tracking, real-time GPS, online booking portal, and integration capabilities with corporate systems.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">✓ Dedicated Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Personal account managers for corporate clients and responsive support team for all booking needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Our Commitment to Safety</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Safety is not just a priority—it's the foundation of our operation. Every aspect of our business is designed with safety in mind:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>All chauffeurs undergo comprehensive background checks including criminal history, driving records, and employment verification</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>Regular drug testing and continuous driving record monitoring for all chauffeurs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>Vehicles maintained on schedules exceeding manufacturer recommendations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>Comprehensive insurance coverage exceeding industry standards</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>Advanced safety features including collision avoidance systems, lane departure warning, and more</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">•</span>
            <span>24/7 dispatch monitoring and support for all vehicles in operation</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white rounded-xl p-8 mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Serving Chicago's Business Community</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We're proud to serve corporations, law firms, financial institutions, consulting firms, and business professionals throughout the Chicago metropolitan area. Our deep understanding of Chicago's business landscape, combined with our commitment to excellence, makes us the trusted transportation partner for the region's most demanding clients.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <span>✓ Downtown Chicago</span>
          <span>✓ River North</span>
          <span>✓ West Loop</span>
          <span>✓ Fulton Market</span>
          <span>✓ Financial District</span>
          <span>✓ Magnificent Mile</span>
          <span>✓ O'Hare Area</span>
          <span>✓ North Shore</span>
          <span>✓ Western Suburbs</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Experience the Difference</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Whether you need a single airport transfer or comprehensive corporate transportation solutions, we invite you to experience the Chicago Executive Car Service difference.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition shadow-lg inline-block">
            Get Started Today
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+13129980909" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition shadow-lg inline-block">
            Call: (312) 998-0909
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
